<font color="#FF0000">FAREWELL TO COOK BARELA</font><br>
<tt>Thu Aug 28 23:45:44 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Ah Cookie, I wondered when you would rear your head. and Bingo, here you are. Lets just cut to the quick. You and I can not talk to each other. I have nothing to be ashamed about (re. My actions during he war) and I think your actions were horrible. In turn, you have nothing to be ashamed about (during the war) and think your actions were honorible.  We have reached an empass. A block. <br><br>
I can live with that.  I will always be your little commie, and your will always be my macho nazi.  I accept that. Let others choose what they may.  You are the macho rambo with twin machine guns under each arm. I am the commie propagandist with twin mimeograph machines (copiers had yet to be invented) under each are spewing forth propaganda for Uncle Ho.  We will never bridge the gap.  I acknowledge that.  I still stand by my previous post about you, which you failed to address. That's OK, I know you can't answer up to the truth.  So Cook, I will let it go.  CHOW BABY. You are still to hung up, stuck up, and wrapped up in your own trip. You don't want input. You just want agreement. Well budddy, not from me. Never.  So go light em up Cook. Dream your dreams of glory and gory. They are all yours, thank God, cause I don't want one tiny piece of it.<br><br>
It's a shame man, cause most of the cops I have known and helped, were veterans of nam, and we still are life long friends to this day.  I will never count you on that list, because you are so different than them.  They faught the good fight, most of them came home, most of them intact. But none of them act like you.  So, when I measure 50 against 1, the truth is clear.  and the 1 can go.  Bye Bye Cook. I will never respond to you again.  I hope your life brings you peace and tranquility, two qualities you sorely miss.
